msgstr "Seidauk iha kategoria."

msgid "Sell on TimorMart"
msgstr "Fa'an iha TimorMart"

msgid "Create a free seller account and reach buyers across Timor-Leste."
msgstr "Kria konta fa'an-na'in grátis no hetan sosa-na'in sira iha Timor-Leste laran tomak."

msgid "Add a product"
msgstr "Aumenta produtu ida"

msgid "Start selling"
msgstr "Hahú fa'an"

